{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Today I want to talk to you"},{"time":2000,"text":"about ethnic conflict"},{"time":4000,"text":"and civil war."},{"time":6000,"text":"These are not normally the most cheerful of topics,"},{"time":9000,"text":"nor do they generally generate"},{"time":11000,"text":"the kind of good news"},{"time":13000,"text":"that this conference is about."},{"time":16000,"text":"Yet, not only is there at least some good news"},{"time":19000,"text":"to be told about fewer such conflicts now"},{"time":22000,"text":"than two decades ago,"},{"time":24000,"text":"but what is perhaps more important"},{"time":26000,"text":"is that we also have come"},{"time":28000,"text":"to a much better understanding of what can be done"},{"time":31000,"text":"to further reduce the number"},{"time":33000,"text":"of ethnic conflicts and civil wars"},{"time":36000,"text":"and the suffering that they inflict."},{"time":39000,"text":"Three things stand out:"},{"time":41000,"text":"leadership, diplomacy"},{"time":44000,"text":"and institutional design."},{"time":47000,"text":"What I will focus on in my talk"},{"time":49000,"text":"is why they matter, how they matter,"},{"time":52000,"text":"and what we can all do"},{"time":54000,"text":"to make sure that they continue to matter"},{"time":56000,"text":"in the right ways,"},{"time":58000,"text":"that is, how all of us can contribute"},{"time":61000,"text":"to developing and honing the skills"},{"time":64000,"text":"of local and global leaders"},{"time":67000,"text":"to make peace"},{"time":69000,"text":"and to make it last."},{"time":71000,"text":"But let's start at the beginning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74000,"text":"Civil wars have made news headlines"},{"time":76000,"text":"for many decades now,"},{"time":78000,"text":"and ethnic conflicts in particular"},{"time":80000,"text":"have been a near constant presence"},{"time":83000,"text":"as a major international security threat."},{"time":86000,"text":"For nearly two decades now,"},{"time":89000,"text":"the news has been bad"},{"time":91000,"text":"and the images have been haunting."},{"time":94000,"text":"In Georgia, after years of stalemate,"},{"time":97000,"text":"we saw a full-scale resurgence of violence"},{"time":100000,"text":"in August, 2008."},{"time":102000,"text":"This quickly escalated into a five-day war"},{"time":105000,"text":"between Russia and Georgia,"},{"time":107000,"text":"leaving Georgia ever more divided."},{"time":110000,"text":"In Kenya, contested presidential elections in 2007 --"},{"time":113000,"text":"we just heard about them --"},{"time":116000,"text":"quickly led to high levels"},{"time":118000,"text":"of inter-ethnic violence"},{"time":120000,"text":"and the killing and displacement"},{"time":122000,"text":"of thousands of people."},{"time":124000,"text":"In Sri Lanka,"},{"time":126000,"text":"a decades-long civil war"},{"time":128000,"text":"between the Tamil minority"},{"time":130000,"text":"and the Sinhala majority"},{"time":132000,"text":"led to a bloody climax in 2009,"},{"time":135000,"text":"after perhaps as many as 100,000"},{"time":137000,"text":"people had been killed"},{"time":139000,"text":"since 1983."},{"time":141000,"text":"In Kyrgyzstan, just over the last few weeks,"},{"time":144000,"text":"unprecedented levels of violence occurred"},{"time":147000,"text":"between ethnic Kyrgyz"},{"time":149000,"text":"and ethnic Uzbeks."},{"time":151000,"text":"Hundreds have been killed,"},{"time":153000,"text":"and more than 100,000 displaced,"},{"time":156000,"text":"including many ethnic Uzbeks"},{"time":158000,"text":"who fled to neighboring Uzbekistan."},{"time":161000,"text":"In the Middle East,"},{"time":163000,"text":"conflict between Israelis and Palestinians"},{"time":166000,"text":"continues unabated,"},{"time":168000,"text":"and it becomes ever more difficult"},{"time":170000,"text":"to see how, just how"},{"time":173000,"text":"a possible, sustainable solution"},{"time":175000,"text":"can be achieved."},{"time":178000,"text":"Darfur may have slipped from the news headlines,"},{"time":181000,"text":"but the killing and displacement there"},{"time":183000,"text":"continues as well,"},{"time":185000,"text":"and the sheer human misery that it creates"},{"time":188000,"text":"is very hard to fathom."},{"time":190000,"text":"And in Iraq, finally,"},{"time":192000,"text":"violence is on the rise again,"},{"time":195000,"text":"and the country has yet to form a government"},{"time":198000,"text":"four months after"},{"time":200000,"text":"its last parliamentary elections."}]},{"cues":[{"time":205000,"text":"But hang on, this talk is to be about the good news."},{"time":208000,"text":"So are these now the images of the past?"},{"time":212000,"text":"Well, notwithstanding the gloomy pictures"},{"time":215000,"text":"from the Middle East, Darfur,"},{"time":217000,"text":"Iraq, elsewhere,"},{"time":219000,"text":"there is a longer-term trend"},{"time":221000,"text":"that does represent some good news."},{"time":224000,"text":"Over the past two decades, since the end of the Cold War,"},{"time":227000,"text":"there has been an overall decline"},{"time":230000,"text":"in the number of civil wars."},{"time":232000,"text":"Since the high in the early 1990s,"},{"time":235000,"text":"with about 50 such civil wars ongoing,"},{"time":238000,"text":"we now have 30 percent fewer"},{"time":240000,"text":"such conflicts today."},{"time":242000,"text":"The number of people killed in civil wars"},{"time":244000,"text":"also is much lower today"},{"time":247000,"text":"than it was a decade ago or two."},{"time":250000,"text":"But this trend is less unambiguous."},{"time":253000,"text":"The highest level of deaths on the battlefield"},{"time":256000,"text":"was recorded between 1998 and 2001,"},{"time":259000,"text":"with about 80,000 soldiers, policemen and rebels"},{"time":262000,"text":"killed every year."},{"time":264000,"text":"The lowest number of combatant casualties"},{"time":266000,"text":"occurred in 2003,"},{"time":269000,"text":"with just 20,000 killed."},{"time":272000,"text":"Despite the up and down since then,"},{"time":275000,"text":"the overall trend --"},{"time":277000,"text":"and this is the important bit --"},{"time":279000,"text":"clearly points downward"},{"time":281000,"text":"for the past two decades."}]},{"cues":[{"time":284000,"text":"The news about civilian casualties"},{"time":286000,"text":"is also less bad than it used to be."},{"time":288000,"text":"From over 12,000 civilians"},{"time":290000,"text":"deliberately killed in civil wars"},{"time":292000,"text":"in 1997 and 1998,"},{"time":295000,"text":"a decade later,"},{"time":297000,"text":"this figure stands at 4,000."},{"time":300000,"text":"This is a decrease by two-thirds."},{"time":303000,"text":"This decline would be even more obvious"},{"time":305000,"text":"if we factored in the genocide in Rwanda"},{"time":307000,"text":"in 1994."},{"time":309000,"text":"But then 800,000 civilians were slaughtered"},{"time":312000,"text":"in a matter of just a few months."},{"time":315000,"text":"This certainly is an accomplishment"},{"time":317000,"text":"that must never be surpassed."},{"time":320000,"text":"What is also important is to note"},{"time":322000,"text":"that these figures only tell part of the story."},{"time":325000,"text":"They exclude people"},{"time":327000,"text":"that died as a consequence of civil war,"},{"time":329000,"text":"from hunger or disease, for example."},{"time":331000,"text":"And they also do not properly account"},{"time":333000,"text":"for civilian suffering more generally."},{"time":337000,"text":"Torture, rape and ethnic cleansing"},{"time":340000,"text":"have become highly effective,"},{"time":343000,"text":"if often non-lethal, weapons in civil war."},{"time":347000,"text":"To put it differently,"},{"time":349000,"text":"for the civilians that suffer the consequences"},{"time":352000,"text":"of ethnic conflict and civil war,"},{"time":355000,"text":"there is no good war"},{"time":358000,"text":"and there is no bad peace."},{"time":362000,"text":"Thus, even though every civilian killed,"},{"time":364000,"text":"maimed, raped, or tortured is one too many,"},{"time":367000,"text":"the fact that the number"},{"time":369000,"text":"of civilian casualties"},{"time":371000,"text":"is clearly lower today"},{"time":373000,"text":"than it was a decade ago,"},{"time":375000,"text":"is good news."}]},{"cues":[{"time":378000,"text":"So, we have fewer conflicts today"},{"time":380000,"text":"in which fewer people get killed."},{"time":383000,"text":"And the big question, of course,"},{"time":385000,"text":"is why?"},{"time":387000,"text":"In some cases,"},{"time":389000,"text":"there is a military victory of one side."},{"time":391000,"text":"This is a solution of sorts,"},{"time":393000,"text":"but rarely is it one"},{"time":395000,"text":"that comes without human costs"},{"time":397000,"text":"or humanitarian consequences."},{"time":400000,"text":"The defeat of the Tamil Tigers in Sri Lanka"},{"time":403000,"text":"is perhaps the most recent example of this,"},{"time":405000,"text":"but we have seen similar"},{"time":407000,"text":"so-called military solutions"},{"time":410000,"text":"in the Balkans, in the South Caucasus"},{"time":412000,"text":"and across most of Africa."},{"time":415000,"text":"At times, they are complimented"},{"time":417000,"text":"by negotiated settlements,"},{"time":419000,"text":"or at least cease-fire agreements,"},{"time":421000,"text":"and peacekeepers are deployed."},{"time":423000,"text":"But hardly ever do they represent"},{"time":425000,"text":"a resounding success --"},{"time":427000,"text":"Bosnia and Herzegovina"},{"time":429000,"text":"perhaps more so than Georgia."},{"time":431000,"text":"But for many parts of Africa,"},{"time":433000,"text":"a colleague of mine once put it this way,"},{"time":436000,"text":"\"The cease-fire on Tuesday night"},{"time":439000,"text":"was reached just in time"},{"time":441000,"text":"for the genocide to start on Wednesday morning.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":446000,"text":"But let's look at the good news again."},{"time":448000,"text":"If there's no solution on the battlefield,"},{"time":450000,"text":"three factors can account"},{"time":452000,"text":"for the prevention of ethnic conflict and civil war,"},{"time":456000,"text":"or for sustainable peace afterwards:"},{"time":459000,"text":"leadership, diplomacy"},{"time":461000,"text":"and institutional design."},{"time":464000,"text":"Take the example of Northern Ireland."},{"time":467000,"text":"Despite centuries of animosity,"},{"time":469000,"text":"decades of violence"},{"time":471000,"text":"and thousands of people killed,"},{"time":474000,"text":"1998 saw the conclusion"},{"time":476000,"text":"of an historic agreement."},{"time":479000,"text":"Its initial version was skillfully mediated"},{"time":482000,"text":"by Senator George Mitchell."},{"time":484000,"text":"Crucially, for the long-term success"},{"time":486000,"text":"of the peace process in Northern Ireland,"},{"time":489000,"text":"he imposed very clear conditions"},{"time":491000,"text":"for the participation and negotiations."},{"time":494000,"text":"Central among them,"},{"time":496000,"text":"a commitment"},{"time":498000,"text":"to exclusively peaceful means."},{"time":501000,"text":"Subsequent revisions of the agreement"},{"time":503000,"text":"were facilitated by the British and Irish governments,"},{"time":506000,"text":"who never wavered in their determination"},{"time":509000,"text":"to bring peace and stability to Northern Ireland."}]},{"cues":[{"time":512000,"text":"The core institutions"},{"time":514000,"text":"that were put in place in 1998"},{"time":516000,"text":"and their modifications"},{"time":518000,"text":"in 2006 and 2008"},{"time":520000,"text":"were highly innovative"},{"time":522000,"text":"and allowed all conflict parties"},{"time":525000,"text":"to see their core concerns and demands addressed."},{"time":529000,"text":"The agreement combines a power-sharing arrangement"},{"time":531000,"text":"in Northern Ireland"},{"time":533000,"text":"with cross-border institutions"},{"time":535000,"text":"that link Belfast and Dublin"},{"time":537000,"text":"and thus recognizes"},{"time":539000,"text":"the so-called Irish dimension of the conflict."},{"time":542000,"text":"And significantly,"},{"time":544000,"text":"there's also a clear focus"},{"time":546000,"text":"on both the rights of individuals"},{"time":548000,"text":"and the rights of communities."},{"time":552000,"text":"The provisions in the agreement may be complex,"},{"time":555000,"text":"but so is the underlying conflict."},{"time":559000,"text":"Perhaps most importantly,"},{"time":561000,"text":"local leaders repeatedly rose to the challenge of compromise,"},{"time":565000,"text":"not always fast"},{"time":567000,"text":"and not always enthusiastically,"},{"time":570000,"text":"but rise in the end they did."},{"time":572000,"text":"Who ever could have imagined"},{"time":575000,"text":"Ian Paisley and Martin McGuinness"},{"time":578000,"text":"jointly governing Northern Ireland"},{"time":580000,"text":"as First and Deputy First Minister?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":583000,"text":"But then, is Northern Ireland a unique example,"},{"time":586000,"text":"or does this kind of explanation"},{"time":588000,"text":"only hold more generally"},{"time":590000,"text":"in democratic and developed countries?"},{"time":593000,"text":"By no means."},{"time":595000,"text":"The ending of Liberia's long-lasting civil war"},{"time":598000,"text":"in 2003"},{"time":600000,"text":"illustrates the importance"},{"time":602000,"text":"of leadership, diplomacy"},{"time":604000,"text":"and institutional design"},{"time":606000,"text":"as much as the successful prevention"},{"time":608000,"text":"of a full-scale civil war"},{"time":610000,"text":"in Macedonia in 2001,"},{"time":613000,"text":"or the successful ending"},{"time":615000,"text":"of the conflict in Aceh in Indonesia in 2005."},{"time":619000,"text":"In all three cases,"},{"time":621000,"text":"local leaders were willing and able"},{"time":623000,"text":"to make peace,"},{"time":625000,"text":"the international community stood ready"},{"time":628000,"text":"to help them negotiate and implement an agreement,"},{"time":631000,"text":"and the institutions have lived up"},{"time":634000,"text":"to the promise that they held"},{"time":636000,"text":"on the day they were agreed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":638000,"text":"Focusing on leadership, diplomacy"},{"time":640000,"text":"and institutional design"},{"time":642000,"text":"also helps explain failures to achieve peace,"},{"time":645000,"text":"or to make it last."},{"time":647000,"text":"The hopes that were vested in the Oslo Accords"},{"time":649000,"text":"did not lead to an end"},{"time":651000,"text":"of the Israeli/Palestinian conflict."},{"time":653000,"text":"Not all the issues that needed to be resolved"},{"time":656000,"text":"were actually covered in the agreements."},{"time":658000,"text":"Rather, local leaders committed"},{"time":661000,"text":"to revisiting them later on."},{"time":664000,"text":"Yet instead of grasping this opportunity,"},{"time":666000,"text":"local and international leaders"},{"time":668000,"text":"soon disengaged"},{"time":670000,"text":"and became distracted"},{"time":672000,"text":"by the second Intifada, the events of 9/11"},{"time":675000,"text":"and the wars in Afghanistan and Iraq."}]},{"cues":[{"time":679000,"text":"The comprehensive peace agreement for Sudan"},{"time":681000,"text":"signed in 2005"},{"time":683000,"text":"turned out to be less comprehensive than envisaged,"},{"time":686000,"text":"and its provisions may yet bear the seeds"},{"time":689000,"text":"of a full-scale return to war"},{"time":691000,"text":"between north and south."},{"time":693000,"text":"Changes and shortcomings in leadership,"},{"time":696000,"text":"more off than on international diplomacy"},{"time":699000,"text":"and institutional failures"},{"time":701000,"text":"account for this"},{"time":703000,"text":"in almost equal measure."},{"time":705000,"text":"Unresolved boundary issues, squabbles over oil revenues,"},{"time":708000,"text":"the ongoing conflict in Darfur,"},{"time":710000,"text":"escalating tribal violence in the south"},{"time":713000,"text":"and generally weak state capacity"},{"time":715000,"text":"across all of Sudan"},{"time":717000,"text":"complete a very depressing picture"},{"time":720000,"text":"of the state of affairs"},{"time":722000,"text":"in Africa's largest country."}]},{"cues":[{"time":724000,"text":"A final example: Kosovo."},{"time":726000,"text":"The failure to achieve"},{"time":728000,"text":"a negotiated solution for Kosovo"},{"time":730000,"text":"and the violence, tension"},{"time":732000,"text":"and de facto partition that resulted from it"},{"time":735000,"text":"have their reasons"},{"time":737000,"text":"in many, many different factors."},{"time":740000,"text":"Central among them are three."},{"time":743000,"text":"First, the intransigence of local leaders"},{"time":746000,"text":"to settle for nothing less"},{"time":748000,"text":"than their maximum demands."},{"time":751000,"text":"Second, an international diplomatic effort"},{"time":754000,"text":"that was hampered from the beginning"},{"time":757000,"text":"by Western support for Kosovo's independence."},{"time":761000,"text":"And third, a lack of imagination"},{"time":764000,"text":"when it came to designing institutions"},{"time":767000,"text":"that could have addressed the concerns"},{"time":769000,"text":"of Serbs and Albanians alike."},{"time":772000,"text":"By the same token --"},{"time":774000,"text":"and here we have some good news again --"},{"time":776000,"text":"the very fact that there is a high-level,"},{"time":779000,"text":"well-resourced international presence"},{"time":781000,"text":"in Kosovo"},{"time":783000,"text":"and the Balkans region more generally"},{"time":786000,"text":"and the fact that local leaders on both sides"},{"time":788000,"text":"have showed relative restraint,"},{"time":790000,"text":"explains why things have not been worse"},{"time":793000,"text":"over the past two years since 2008."}]},{"cues":[{"time":796000,"text":"So even in situations"},{"time":798000,"text":"where outcomes are less than optimal,"},{"time":801000,"text":"local leaders"},{"time":803000,"text":"and international leaders have a choice,"},{"time":806000,"text":"and they can make a difference for the better."},{"time":809000,"text":"A cold war"},{"time":811000,"text":"is not as good"},{"time":813000,"text":"as a cold peace,"},{"time":815000,"text":"but a cold peace"},{"time":817000,"text":"is still better than a hot war."},{"time":821000,"text":"Good news is also about learning the right lesson."},{"time":824000,"text":"So what then distinguishes"},{"time":826000,"text":"the Israeli/Palestinian conflict"},{"time":828000,"text":"from that in Northern Ireland,"},{"time":831000,"text":"or the civil war in Sudan"},{"time":833000,"text":"from that in Liberia?"},{"time":835000,"text":"Both successes and failures"},{"time":838000,"text":"teach us several critically important things"},{"time":841000,"text":"that we need to bear in mind"},{"time":843000,"text":"if we want the good news to continue."},{"time":845000,"text":"First, leadership."},{"time":848000,"text":"In the same way in which ethnic conflict and civil war"},{"time":852000,"text":"are not natural"},{"time":854000,"text":"but man-made disasters,"},{"time":856000,"text":"their prevention and settlement"},{"time":858000,"text":"does not happen automatically either."},{"time":862000,"text":"Leadership needs to be capable,"},{"time":865000,"text":"determined and visionary"},{"time":867000,"text":"in its commitment to peace."},{"time":869000,"text":"Leaders need to connect to each other"},{"time":872000,"text":"and to their followers,"},{"time":874000,"text":"and they need to bring them along"},{"time":876000,"text":"on what is an often arduous journey"},{"time":879000,"text":"into a peaceful future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":881000,"text":"Second, diplomacy."},{"time":884000,"text":"Diplomacy needs to be well resourced,"},{"time":887000,"text":"sustained,"},{"time":889000,"text":"and apply the right mix of incentives and pressures"},{"time":891000,"text":"on leaders and followers."},{"time":893000,"text":"It needs to help them reach an equitable compromise,"},{"time":896000,"text":"and it needs to ensure"},{"time":898000,"text":"that a broad coalition"},{"time":900000,"text":"of local, regional"},{"time":902000,"text":"and international supporters"},{"time":904000,"text":"help them implement their agreement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":907000,"text":"Third, institutional design."},{"time":910000,"text":"Institutional design requires"},{"time":912000,"text":"a keen focus on issues,"},{"time":914000,"text":"innovative thinking"},{"time":916000,"text":"and flexible and well-funded implementation."},{"time":920000,"text":"Conflict parties need to move away"},{"time":923000,"text":"from maximum demands"},{"time":925000,"text":"and towards a compromise"},{"time":927000,"text":"that recognizes each other's needs."},{"time":930000,"text":"And they need to think"},{"time":932000,"text":"about the substance of their agreement"},{"time":934000,"text":"much more than about"},{"time":936000,"text":"the labels they want to attach to them."},{"time":938000,"text":"Conflict parties also need to be prepared"},{"time":940000,"text":"to return to the negotiation table"},{"time":943000,"text":"if the agreement implementation stalls."}]},{"cues":[{"time":947000,"text":"For me personally,"},{"time":949000,"text":"the most critical lesson of all is this:"},{"time":952000,"text":"Local commitment to peace"},{"time":954000,"text":"is all-important,"},{"time":956000,"text":"but it is often not enough"},{"time":959000,"text":"to prevent or end violence."},{"time":962000,"text":"Yet, no amount of diplomacy"},{"time":965000,"text":"or institutional design"},{"time":967000,"text":"can make up for local failures"},{"time":970000,"text":"and the consequences that they have."},{"time":973000,"text":"Therefore, we must invest"},{"time":976000,"text":"in developing leaders,"},{"time":979000,"text":"leaders that have the skills,"},{"time":982000,"text":"vision and determination"},{"time":984000,"text":"to make peace."},{"time":986000,"text":"Leaders, in other words,"},{"time":988000,"text":"that people will trust"},{"time":990000,"text":"and that they will want to follow"},{"time":993000,"text":"even if that means"},{"time":995000,"text":"making hard choices."}]},{"cues":[{"time":998000,"text":"A final thought:"},{"time":1000000,"text":"Ending civil wars"},{"time":1002000,"text":"is a process that is fraught with dangers,"},{"time":1005000,"text":"frustrations and setbacks."},{"time":1008000,"text":"It often takes a generation to accomplish,"},{"time":1011000,"text":"but it also requires us, today's generation,"},{"time":1014000,"text":"to take responsibility"},{"time":1016000,"text":"and to learn the right lessons"},{"time":1018000,"text":"about leadership, diplomacy"},{"time":1021000,"text":"and institutional design,"},{"time":1024000,"text":"so that the child soldiers of today"},{"time":1027000,"text":"can become the children of tomorrow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1029000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1031000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}